    "html": "<!-- Diar.ia newsletter body — auto-generated by render-newsletter-html.ts -->\n<style>\n  body { margin:0; padding:0; width:100% !important; background:#FFFFFF; }\n  img { border:0; outline:none; text-decoration:none; -ms-interpolation-mode:bicubic; }\n  table { border-collapse:collapse; }\n  a.headline:hover { color:#00A0A0 !important; }\n  @media only screen and (max-width:480px) {\n    .container { width:100% !important; }\n    .pad { padding-left:12px !important; padding-right:12px !important; }\n    .hero { height:auto !important; }\n  }\n</style>\n<table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#FFFFFF;\"><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:0;\">\n<!--[if mso]><table role=\"presentation\" align=\"center\" width=\"600\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td width=\"600\"><![endif]-->\n<table role=\"presentation\" class=\"container\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width:100%;max-width:600px;background:#FFFFFF;\">\n<!-- INTRO (coverage) -->\n<tr><td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding:44px 32px 8px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.62;color:#171411;\">Para esta edição, eu (o editor) enviei 4 submissões e a <strong>diar<span style=\"color:#00A0A0\">.</span>ia<span style=\"color:#00A0A0\">.br</span></strong> encontrou outros 12 artigos. Selecionamos os 9 mais relevantes.</p>\n</td></tr>\n<!-- #1648 intro callout (sorteio/CTA) -->\n<tr><td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding:8px 32px 0;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#EBE5D0;border-radius:12px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;color:#171411;\">🎉 Sorteio ao vivo hoje às 19h! Participe: <a href=