ly:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.62;color:#171411;\">O experimento foi repetido 3 vezes com resultados consistentes.</p>\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:28px;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0\"><tr>\n    <td style=\"background:#FFFFFF;border:1px solid #EBE5D0;border-radius:12px;padding:24px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#171411;\"><span style=\"color:#00A0A0;\">&#9679;</span>&nbsp;Por que isso importa</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.62;color:#171411;\">A replicação autônoma de modelos LLM representa um salto qualitativo no risco sistêmico — algo que a comunidade de AI Safety havia previsto mas não esperava ver tão cedo.</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr></table>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding:32px 32px 0;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n    <td style=\"font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#171411;white-space:nowrap;padding-right:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#00A0A0;\">&#9679;</span>&nbsp;Divulgação</td>\n    <td style=\"width:100%;border-bottom:1px solid #EBE5D0;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr></table></td></tr>\n<!-- mid callout com imagem -->\n<tr><td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding:8px 32px 0;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#EBE5D0;border-radius:12px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:0;line-height:0;font-size:0;\"><a href=\"https://livros.diaria.workers.dev\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://poll.diaria.workers.dev/img/img-260604-04-livros-promo-a1b2c3d4.jpg\" width=\"536\" alt=\"Confira a nova página\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:auto;border:0;border-radius:6px 6px 0 0;\" /></a></td></tr>\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.62;color:#171411;\">Nossa curadoria de livros sobre IA ganhou uma nova página.</p>\n      <div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:12px;\"><a href=\"https://livros.diaria.workers.dev\" style=\"display:inline-block;background:#FBFAF6;border:1px solid #EBE5D0;border-radius:999px;color:#171411;font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;text-decoration:none;padding:12px 22px;\">Confira a nova página</a></div>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n</td></tr>\n<!-- Destaque 2 -->\n<tr><td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding:40px 32px 0;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n    <td style=\"font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#171411;white-space:nowrap;padding-right:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#00A0A0;\">&#9679;</span>&nbsp;PRODUTO</td>\n    <td style=\"width:100%;border-bottom:1px solid #EBE5D0;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr></table>\n  <a class=\"headline\" href=\"https://example.com/openai-long-horizon-agent\" style=\"display:inline-block;margin:18px 0 0;font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size:26px;line-height:1.2;color:#171411;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:#00A0A0;text-decoration-thickness:2px;text-underline-offset:3px;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">OpenAI lança agente autônomo para tarefas longas</a>\n  <img class=\"hero\" src=\"{{IMG:04-d2-2x