Font, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#171411;\"><span style=\"color:#00A0A0;\">&#9679;</span>&nbsp;Por que isso importa</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.62;color:#171411;\">Primeira lei abrangente de IA no mundo — vai moldar como produtos de IA operam na Europa e influenciar legislações globais.</p>\n    </td>\n  </tr></table>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding:32px 32px 0;\"><table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n    <td style=\"font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#171411;white-space:nowrap;padding-right:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#00A0A0;\">&#9679;</span>&nbsp;Divulgação</td>\n    <td style=\"width:100%;border-bottom:1px solid #EBE5D0;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr></table></td></tr>\n<!-- #1648 intro callout (sorteio/CTA) -->\n<tr><td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding:8px 32px 0;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#EBE5D0;border-radius:12px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5;color:#171411;\">🔧 Indicação de ferramenta: uso o Raycast todo dia pra automatizar buscas. <a href=\"https://raycast.com\" style=\"color:#171411;text-decoration:underline;text-decoration-color:#00A0A0;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Confira</a>.</p>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n</td></tr>\n<!-- LANÇAMENTOS -->\n<tr><td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding:40px 32px 0;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n    <td style