xample.com/cursor-style-guide\" style=\"font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size:22px;line-height:1.14;color:#171411;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid #00A0A0;\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\">Como configurar o Cursor para manter um estilo de código consistente</a>\n      <p style=\"margin:7px 0 0;font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.62;color:#171411;\">Arquivo .cursorrules + instruções de contexto que reduzem revisões manuais.</p>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n</td></tr>\n<!-- É IA? (poll) -->\n<tr><td class=\"pad\" style=\"padding:40px 32px 0;\">\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr>\n    <td style=\"font-family:'Geist', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, system-ui, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#171411;white-space:nowrap;padding-right:12px;\"><span style=\"color:#00A0A0;\">&#9679;</span>&nbsp;É IA?</td>\n    <td style=\"width:100%;border-bottom:1px solid #EBE5D0;font-size:0;line-height:0;\">&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr></table>\n  <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:22px;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:0\"><tr>\n    <td style=\"background:#EBE5D0;border-radius:12px;padding:24px 28px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-family:Georgia, 'Times New Roman', serif;font-size:26px;line-height:1.2;color:#171411;\">Clique na imagem que foi gerada por IA</p>\n      <table role=\"presentation\" width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-top:22px;\">\n        <tr><td><a href=\"https://poll.diaria.workers.dev/vote?email={{email}}&edition=260999&choice=A\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"{{IMG:01-eia-A.jpg}}\" alt=\"Imagem A\" width=\"480\" style=\"display:block;width:100%;height:auto;border-radius:6px;\" borde